The supported Transaction fields are: AccountId, Accuracy, Amount, AmountInCurrency, Balance,BankId, CategoryChangedTime, CategoryId, Date, DueDate, HasUserClearedCategoryUncertainty, Id, IsFlagged,IsMerchant, IsOwnAccountTransfer, IsRead, IsSplitChild, IsUncleared, InsertTime, Mcc, MerchantId, ParentIdentifier, Text, Timestamp, CounterpartyAccountIdentifier, Currency, HasUncertainCategorization, OriginalAmount, OriginalDate, OriginalText
